de: Memorandum of Understanding regarding the Convention between the Swiss Confederation and the Argentine Republic for the Avoidance of Double Taxation with Respect to Taxes on Income and on Capital and the Protocol thereto - 16-11-2016 - Abkommen vom 20. März 2014 zwischen der Schweizerischen Eidgenossenschaft und der Republik Argentinien zur Vermeidung der Doppelbesteuerung auf dem Gebiet der Steuern vom Einkommen und vom Vermögen (mit Prot.)
en: Memorandum of Understanding regarding the Convention between the Swiss Confederation and the Argentine Republic for the Avoidance of Double Taxation with Respect to Taxes on Income and on Capital and the Protocol thereto - 16-11-2016 - Convention between the Swiss Confederation and the Argentine Republic for the Avoidance of Double Taxation with Respect to Taxes on Income and on Capital
it: Memorandum of Understanding regarding the Convention between the Swiss Confederation and the Argentine Republic for the Avoidance of Double Taxation with Respect to Taxes on Income and on Capital and the Protocol thereto - 16-11-2016 - Convenzione del 20 marzo 2014 tra la Confederazione Svizzera e la Repubblica Argentina per evitare le doppie imposizioni in materia di imposte sul reddito e sul patrimonio (con Prot.)
fr: Memorandum of Understanding regarding the Convention between the Swiss Confederation and the Argentine Republic for the Avoidance of Double Taxation with Respect to Taxes on Income and on Capital and the Protocol thereto - 16-11-2016 - Convention du 20 mars 2014 entre la Confédération suisse et la République argentine en vue d'éviter les doubles impositions en matière d'impôts sur le revenu et sur la fortune (avec prot.)
